'''''Stand in Line''''' is the first studio album by [[heavy metal music|heavy metal]] band [[Impellitteri]], released in 1988 through [[Relativity Records]]; a [[remaster]]ed edition was reissued in 2009 through [[EMI Records]], containing four bonus tracks which originally formed their [[Impellitteri (album)|1987 self-titled EP]].<ref>[http://www.cduniverse.com/productinfo.asp?pid=7939205 "Impellitteri - Stand In Line CD"]. ''CD Universe''. [[Muze]]. Retrieved 2012-09-24.</ref>

